data.meta_description:
2,177 likes, 32 comments - patekworld_ on June 15, 2024: "The last Shah/King of the Imperial State of Iran, late Mohammad Reza Pahlavi @officialrezapahlavi, is in this 1979 photo wearing a vintage Patek Philippe "Jumbo" Nautilus reference 3700/1J from 1978, which was only the third year of this models production.

It features a 42 mm case in 18k yellow gold surrounding a black dial, fully linked with the more sought after 'wider' bracelet.

Price market: $210,000.00 USD
